MaxTechBD School ERP - Fee Management Engine
===========================================

Version: v3.0-final-stable
Build: Stable – MaxTechBD Fee Engine
Release Date: October 23, 2025
Status: PRODUCTION-READY ✅

Critical Components (Protected):
- Fee Management System
- Student Fees Automation
- Payment Collection Engine
- Real-time Fee Due Updates

Verified Features:
✅ Automatic student_fees generation on configuration create/update
✅ Smart pending amount recalculation (preserves payment history)
✅ Real-time Fee Due tab updates (removes students after full payment)
✅ ERP payment logic (overdue → pending → advance)
✅ Multi-tenant data isolation with is_active filtering
✅ Soft-delete protection for historical records

Protected Fields & Filters:
⚠️ StudentFee.is_active: bool = True (DO NOT REMOVE)
⚠️ All student_fees queries MUST include "is_active": True filter
⚠️ Payment queries MUST filter for active records only

Technical Debt Status: ZERO
Known Issues: NONE
Regression Risk: LOW (with protection rules enforced)

Breaking Changes from v2.x:
- Added mandatory is_active field to StudentFee model
- All student_fees queries now require is_active filter
- Payment collection targets active records only

Migration Notes:
- Existing student_fees records without is_active will be excluded from queries
- Run manual data migration to add is_active=True to old records if needed
- No schema changes required for new installations

Maintenance Guidelines:
1. Never remove is_active field from StudentFee model
2. Never remove is_active filter from student_fees queries
3. Always test payment collection after any fee-related changes
4. Verify Fee Due tab updates in real-time after modifications

Build Verified By: MaxTechBD Development Team
Last Tested: October 23, 2025
Deployment Environment: Replit Production
